\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I can expound here if I need to.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 For many we don\'92t want FREEDOM\'85we want FREEDOM from RESPONSIBILITY\uc0\u8232 \
