\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I want to be able to sleep with whoever I want\'85to which God would say\'85you can! \'a0There are just consequences.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I want to be able to do whatever I want\'85you can\'85there are just consequences with each decision\uc0\u8232 \
